Package info.interactivesystems.gamificationengine.entities.present

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Board
    A Board serves a player to store presents in three lists: When a present is sent to a player firstly it is added to the inBox-list.
    ImageMessage
    A present can be an imageMessage in the form of an image icon with a positive message for the receiver.
    Present
    A present is a little positive message which one player can send to one or more other players.
    PresentAccepted
    Presents that are in the in-box of the board a player can accept or deny.
    PresentArchived
    Presents that are accepted a player can archived.
    TextMessage
    A present can be a short positive text message, which is sent to one or more receivers.
